secubox-glances (1.0.0-1~bookworm1) bookworm; urgency=medium

  * Initial release - Glances system monitoring module.
  * FastAPI backend with psutil-based stats collection.
  * Endpoints: status, health, stats, processes, sensors, history.
  * Service control: start, stop, restart glances daemon.
  * Configuration management via TOML.
  * P31 Phosphor light theme frontend.
  * Tabs: Dashboard, Processes, Sensors, Config.
  * Real-time graphs for CPU/Memory/Network.

